      "id": "f0effff028ce6020",
      "text": "\nMARSHALL, Stuart M., MOORE, Douglas G., MURRAY, Alastair R. G., WALKER, Sara I. and CRONIN, Leroy, 2022. Formalising the Pathways to Life Using Assembly Spaces. Entropy. Online. July 2022. Vol. 24, no. 7, p. 884. [Accessed 15 July 2022]. DOI 10.3390/e24070884. "
